### 1. **iPhone SE (3rd Generation)**

The iPhone SE (3rd Gen) continues to be a top choice in 2026. Originally released in 2022, this compact device combines Apple’s classic design with modern hardware.

**Key Features:**  
- A15 Bionic chip for exceptional speed  
- 4.7-inch Retina HD display  
- Touch ID for secure and convenient unlocking  
- 12MP rear camera with Smart HDR 4  

**Why It’s Great:**  
The iPhone SE (3rd Gen) is ideal for those who prefer smaller phones without compromising on performance. Plus, it’s one of the most affordable ways to enjoy 5G connectivity.  

**Price in 2026:** Starting at $429  

